system works best on the 15 min for mnq. looking for a break of the opening range and the overnight range then selling above the prior bar high or buying below the prior bar low. So buying a pullback after a breakout about above the range or sells prior bar high after the breakout below the range. You can mess with stop and target sizes time cut offs and such. Hope it helps
